						<li><a href="#whats_marugoto1" class="target-link active two-rows" rel="whats_marugoto">"Marugoto:Japanese<br />language and culture"</a></li>
						<li><a href="#whats_marugoto2" class="target-link" rel="whats_marugoto">About the JF Standard</a></li>
